  Task "<%= a.trackable.name %>" was added by <%= a.owner.first_name %> <%= a.owner.last_name %> <%= time_ago_in_words(a.created_at.to_time) %> ago.
<% else %>
  Task was added by <%= a.owner.first_name %> <%= a.owner.last_name %>which has since been removed <%= time_ago_in_words(a.created_at.to_time) %> ago.
<% end %>
